item.title: Argoury 666 || Grand Exchange || Construction || Quests
item.dc:creator: @popcorn57 popcorn57
item.description:
@popcorn57 wrote:

Awesome server, Just created my account today. Awesome customization in the game. Even down to game modes and XP rates. I chose the “Hard” xp difficulty which also gives you a drop rate boost so I am not disappointed with the great drops I am getting!

Has an amazing world layout as well with different training and skilling areas with cool brand new interfaces!

Has a new teleporting system not just your regular layout like how it is on other servers.

And staff is very friendly and helpful. And it has the perfect money making rate in the game with a great eco!

It is totally worth the download come check it out.
